EN: She spends a long time washing up every night.

ZH: 他匆匆忙忙地洗漱完，就赶去上班了。
EN: He quickly washed up and rushed to work.

ZH: 我喜欢在洗漱后刷牙。
EN: I like to brush my teeth after washing up.

